December 9, 1968.

No. -.

Granello, aka Burns v. United States. Irving Anolik for applicant. Solicitor General Griswold for the United States in opposition.

C. A. 2d Cir. Application for bail presented to Mr. Justice Harlan, and by him referred to the Court, denied.

Mr. Justice Brennan and Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
